<h2>Research Themes</h2>

<p>Themes summarise projects present in the OSB related to specific areas of neuronal modelling, e.g. a particular brain region or a disease state.</p>
<p>Offers of help to curate these are very welcome, as are suggestions for Themes to add. Please <a href="mailto:info@opensourcebrain.org">get in contaxct</a>.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

